asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Max Flufatansky
description:
I grew up in the Aussie desert during tough times when the country was on the verge of societal collapse. There were critical resource shortages and war broke out. I had to fend for myself, as my parents were killed by a gang of degenerates. I was only 21. 
Unfortunately I wasn’t the only fluf who lost loved ones and as I moved from burrow to burrow in hiding, I came across other lost souls and we banded together and created our own fluf singlet gang. 
My whistle is our gathering call, so keep one of your big ears out for its sound.
Yellow is the color for hope and positivity, it’s all we have. 
My mission now is to find as many flufs lost in the desert and bring them into the fold and create our new metaverse of hope and love. I thought I saw my Angelbaby3045 once but it must have been a mirage but I'll keep looking.
The symbol on our singlets displays our 'peace' sign.  PEACE OUT Flufs!

name: Buster
description:
Buster is known as an enforcer. His loyalty is unmatched and he will do anything for Rizzla and the rest of the clan. He’s been hardened through his years of combat after the wreck, and has made himself known as one fluf you just don’t mess with, especially since he was one of Thumpers top lieutenants. He and Thumper went through it all together, and they’ve maintained a weekly catch up for a beer at Hoppy’s Bar ever since. 
But Buster isn’t all macho tough guy... you can see it in his eyes, on the inside he’s a big softie. He’s a lover as well as a fighter. 
When back in the burrow, he likes to remove his hardened shell and keep the fluflets entertained with tricks and jokes. It’s his way to find some balance in his life.
One mistake you don’t ever want to make is to take Busters red clown nose, and love of a sweet sugary treat, as any form of weakness... because he will fluf you up!

name: Cupid
description:
The Fluf God of Love.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

I am here to educate you on this topic and change your life for the better.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: It’s not easy being voted FLUF WORLDS most eligible rabbit, the pressure it puts on me to look my Fluffen best every day is sometimes too much. This will be the 1,651st time I have won it in a row and sometimes being the beauty queen of FLUF World is great and other times I feel like the men just look at me like a piece of carrot. This leads me to just hang out in my high roller burrow all day long which as you can imagine isn’t that bad at all. I have featured in all the top magazines like The FLUF street Journal, Fluffen News First, FLUFS illustrated, New FLUF Times and Desperate FLUF Wives. Sure, I admit it, I love the attention but I tell you one thing is for sure, I love the sweet, sweet nectar of Mycelium. The love potion of FLUF World and the reason why we are all still here.
